title: Hitachi HNAS: Virtual Servers (EVS)
agents: hitachi_hnas_rest
catalog: hw/storagehw/hitachi
license: GPLv2
distribution: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH
description:
 This check monitors the virtual servers (EVS) of a Hitachi NAS
 (HNAS) system via the File Storage REST API. It requires the
 special agent "Hitachi HNAS via REST API" to be configured for
 the host.

 The service is OK if the virtual server is ONLINE, WARN if it is
 DISABLED, CRIT if it is OFFLINE and UNKNOWN if it is
 NOT_CONFIGURED. If a discovered virtual server is disabled by the
 administrator, the service goes WARN.

item:
 The name of the virtual server.

discovery:
 One service is created for each enabled virtual server.
